SECTION 1 — THE CONDITION
-------------------------
The rights granted in Section 2 are offered to you on the single condition
that you have starred the canonical repository at:

    https://github.com/superturtlee/anland

"Starred" means your GitHub account shows an active star on that repository
at the time you obtain, copy, build, run, or distribute the Software.

If you have not starred the repository, NO rights are granted to you under
this license. Any reproduction, use, modification, or distribution of the
Software without a star is unauthorized and constitutes infringement of the
copyright holder's exclusive rights (informally: "piracy").


